document_data.name: Redethemar
document_data.mainbody:
'''Redethemar''' was a magical [[axe]] possessed by [[Ilianaro Durothil]] around [[1367 DR]].

It was the greatest weapon of House [[Durothil]]. The axe was said to contain the spirit of an [[elf|elven]] goddess.
